title: Having trouble identifying these
author: lostineverfreeforest

comments.content:
"EVERFREE NORTHWEST attendee" is **Bigfish (Black)** free font by Felix Braden [Floodfonts, 2009]:  
 [http://www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/Bigfish](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317145434/http:/www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/Bigfish "http://www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/Bigfish")

"K.K.Slider" is **[Maiden Orange](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317145434/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Google-Web-Fonts%20%2F%20%28Freemium%29&ffam=Maiden%20Orange%20-%20Regular&fid=d7a4b548e75d2ea2e8a5052c38c8af7b&fsize=60&text=K.K.Slider&wrap=2)** by Brian J. Bonislawsky [DBA Astigmatic, 2010] now part of Google Web Fonts
